---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Karen Arze | Home">
    <section style="display: flex; gap: 60px; margin-bottom: 80px; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        
        <div style="flex: 1.5; min-width: 300px;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 4rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1;">Karen Arze</h1>
            <p style="color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 3px; margin: 15px 0 30px 0;">Optical Professional</p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #444; margin-bottom: 40px; border-left: 2px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 20px;">
                Quick to adapt and eager to learn, I am reliable enough to take on leadership roles and always strive for work that can model what I would like to see in others. I'm always enthusiastic to apply my experiences into an environment that appreciates organization and efficiency!
            </p>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding-top: 30px;">
                <div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Location</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--navy); margin: 0; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: bold;">Norfolk, Virginia</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Phone Number</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--navy); margin: 0; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: bold;">757-515-****</p>
                </div>
                <div style="grid-column: span 2;">
                    <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 5px 0;">Email</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--navy); margin: 0; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: bold;">karen_nat*@yahoo.com</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 320px; text-align: center;">
            <div style="width: 100%; max-width: 380px; height: 500px; background: #f0f0f0; border: 1px solid var(--gold); padding: 12px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: -20px 20px 0px rgba(184, 159, 109, 0.1);">
                <img 
                    src="/Arze_K/karen.jpg" 
                    alt="Karen Arze" 
                    style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block;" 
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<h2 style="text-align: center; font-size: 3rem; margin-top: 60px; margin-bottom: 40px; color: var(--navy);">Personal Interests</h2>

<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; align-items: stretch;">
    
    <div style="padding: 30px; background: var(--mist); border: 1px solid var(--gold); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--gold); margin: 0 0 15px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 1.2rem;">The Shoreline</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; color: #444;">Long walks on the beach. Even if it's a bit of a drive, it's always worth being able to see the beautiful sunrise!</p>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px; background: var(--mist); border: 1px solid var(--gold); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--gold); margin: 0 0 15px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 1.2rem;">The Rhythm</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; color: #444;">Dancing—Bachata, Meringue, Jazz, and Salsa. This is when I feel the most like myself!</p>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px; background: var(--mist); border: 1px solid var(--gold); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="color: var(--gold); margin: 0 0 15px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 1.2rem;">The Kitchen</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; color: #444;">Experimental cooking. Challenging myself with available ingredients to create family favorites.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px; background: var(--mist); border: 2px solid var(--navy); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: var(--navy); font-size: 1.2rem;">My Heart ❤️</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; color: #444;">My Son and Daughter are my pride and joy! Though they're grown, they will always be my babies.</p>
    </div>

</div>
</MainLayout>
